@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fffshm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(0.84)
    v0 = ((v1 * 0.39) + ((v1 + 0.12 * v1 + 0.48) * wp.abs(v2 + 0.13)))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.07 + v1 + 0.25)) / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.63) - wp.abs(tmp + 0.81)))
    v2 = 0.19
    v2 = v1
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.exp(tmp + 0.60) - 0.02))
    v1 = v1
    tmp = ((v2 / (v0 + 0.82 - v1 + 0.71)) - ((v2 + 0.98 + v1 + 0.91) / (tmp + 0.03 + v0 + 0.91)))
    data[tid] = v0
